  "title": "Snr Technical Project Manager",
  "description": "<p>1 Supervise and manage installation of railway communication systems .</p><p>2 Hands on experience in Fibre Optic Cable Installation,\n  splicing, termination and ODTR/ power meter testing</p><p>3 Experience in Radio Cable installation, termination and system\n  testing</p><p>4 Co-ordinate with supervise subcontractors and site team.</p><p>5 Ensure work comply with approved drawings and safety\n  requirements<br />6 Carry out site inspection, testing, troubleshoot and\n  commission system</p><p>7 Able to meet time line according to project schedule at same\n  time meeting quality standards and authority requirements</p><p>8 Proficient in AutoCAD</p><p>9 Familiar with Navisworks</p><p>10 Prepare method statement, inspectio test plan, progress report\n  and</p><p>technical documentation</p><p>11 Attend meeting with consultant, contractors and LTA</p><p>12 Able to work in shifts as and when required</p><p>13 Able to work under pressure</p><p>14 Physically and medically fit to work in tunnels and\n     underground environment</p><p>15 Preferred previous experience, about 10 years in MRT? Railway\n     tunnel projects</p><p>16 Good communication skills to all levels</p>",
